# Planning docs (local-only)
# Note: .vbw-planning/ exclusion covers all runtime files inside:
#   - .agent-pids (tmux agent tracking)
#   - .hook-errors.log (hook and cleanup logs, doctor-cleanup.sh runtime logs)
#   - .watchdog-pid (tmux watchdog PID)
#   - .watchdog.log (tmux watchdog logs)
#   - .snapshots/ — agent state snapshots (covered by .vbw-planning/ exclusion)
